OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1778339462
OL,3,CDamaged powerlines disrupt services at
OL,4,CLondon Euston
OL,6,FPassengers face disruption at one of
OL,7,FLondon's busiest railway stations
OL,8,Fafter crucial power lines were damaged.
OL,10,FNetwork Rail has been forced to cut
OL,11,Fthe number of trains to and from
OL,12,FEuston to allow engineers to carry out
OL,13,Frepairs.
OL,15,FThe emergency timetable means fewer
OL,16,Ftrains between London, Birmingham,
OL,17,FLiverpool and Manchester.
OL,19,FAll trains from London which terminate
OL,20,Fat Tring have been cancelled.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/4
