PN,40902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1778339462
OL,3,CDamaged powerlines disrupt services at
OL,4,CLondon Euston
OL,6,FNetwork Rail said the 'complexity of
OL,7,Fthe damage' to the overhead cables
OL,8,Fmeant the disruption would continue
OL,9,Fduring Friday May 7th.
OL,11,FPictures of the damage showed 25,000
OL,12,Fvolt power lines between Watford
OL,13,FJunction and Milton Keynes hanging
OL,14,Fdown.
OL,16,FNetwork Rail's Gary Walsh said: "I am
OL,17,Fsorry to passengers impacted by the
OL,18,Fdamage to overhead powerlines on the
OL,19,FWest Coast Main Line."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/4
