OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1778339462
OL,3,CDamaged powerlines disrupt services at
OL,4,CLondon Euston
OL,6,FHe added: "To carry out a full repair
OL,7,Fand restore our usual service, we need
OL,8,Fto reduce the number of trains
OL,9,Ftravelling along the West Coast Main
OL,10,FLine."
